      <h2 class="h1 best-practice__header">Referring someone in need of help</h2>

      <h2 class="h2">During Office Hours (Tuesday – Thursday 9am - 5pm</h2>

      <p>Approaches are made via physical presentation at Apostles House located at 24 Grant St, Newark, NJ 07104. </p>

      <h2 class="h2">Out of Hours</h2>

      <p>Out of hours placements are made through ‘Out of hours’ response on 973 350-9715.</p>
      <p>The public can also notify the Street Outreach Team in Newark if they are worried about the homeless – contact can be made with at 973 350-9715 or email via on <a href="mailto:victoria.griffith@theapostleshouse.org">victoria.griffith@theapostleshouse.org</a>. The Street Outreach Team work closely with the local authority to obtain suitable accommodation for the homeless and are in operation between 23.00 – 2.00 during the severe weather conditions.</p>
